obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE GIFT-TAX ACT, 1958`
  line ______
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ______
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `C HARGE OF GIFT-TAX AND GIFTS SUBJECT TO SUCH CHARGE`
  line `3. Charge of gift-tax.`
  line `4. Gifts to include certain transfers.`
  line `5. Exemption in respect of certain gifts.`
  line `6. Value of gifts, how determined.`
  line `6A. [ Omitted.].`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `G IFT-TAX AUTHORITIES`
  line `7. Gift-tax authorities and their jurisdiction.`
  line `7A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `7AA. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `7B. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `8. Control of gift-tax authorities.`
  line `8A. [ Omitted.].`
  line `9. Instructions to subordinate authorities.`
  line `9A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `10. Jurisdiction of Assessing Officers and power to transfer cases.`
  line `11. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `11A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `11AA. [ Omitted.].`
  line `11B. [ Omitted.].`
  line `12. [ Omitted.].`
  line `* Subject to verification and confirmation by the Administrative ministry.`
