obj_root_law_sections_53_content:
  string
  line 53
  line `1 [SCHEDULE 2 [I]`
  line `3 [[ See section 3( 1 )]]`
  line `R ATES OF GIFT-TAX`
  line `( 1 ) where the value of all taxable gifts does not`
  line `exceed Rs. 20,000`
  line `5 per cent. of the value of such`
  line gifts;
  line `( 2 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 20,000 but does not exceed Rs. 50,000`
  line `Rs. 1,000 plus 10 per cent. of the`
  line `amount by which the value of such`
  line `gifts exceeds Rs. 20,000;`
  line `( 3 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 50,000 but does not exceed Rs. 1,00,000`
  line `Rs. 4,000 plus 15 per cent. of the`
  line `amount by which the value of such`
  line `gifts exceeds Rs. 50,000;`
  line `( 4 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 1,00,000 but d oes not exceed`
  line `Rs. 2,00,000`
  line `Rs. 11,500 plus 20 per cent. of the`
  line `amount by which the value of such`
  line `gifts exceeds Rs. 1,00,000;`
  line `( 5 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 2,00,000 but does not exceed`
  line `Rs. 5,00,000`
  line `Rs. 31,500 plus 25 per cent. of the`
  line `amount by which the value of such`
  line `gifts exceeds Rs. 2,00,000;`
  line `( 6 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 5,00,000 but does not exceed`
  line `Rs. 10,00,00 0`
  line `Rs. 1,06,500 plus 30 per cent. of`
  line `the amount by which the value of`
  line `such gifts exceeds Rs. 5,00,000;`
  line `( 7 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 10,00,000 but does not exceed`
  line `Rs. 15,00,000`
  line `Rs. 2,56,500 plus 40 per cent. of`
  line `the amount by which the value of`
  line `such gifts exceeds Rs. 10,00,000;`
  line `( 8 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 15,00,000 but does not exceed`
  line `Rs. 20,00,000`
  line `Rs. 4,56,500 plus 50 per cent. of`
  line `the amount by which the value of`
  line `such gifts exceeds Rs. 15,00,000;`
  line `( 9 ) where the value of all taxable gifts exceeds`
  line `Rs. 20,00,000`
  line `Rs. 7,06,500 plus 75 per cent. of`
  line `the amount by which the value of`
  line `such gifts exceeds Rs. 20,00,000.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 27, for the Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).`
  line `2. The Schedule renumbered as the Schedule ( 1 ) thereof by Act 3 of 1989, s. 94 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 23 of 1986, s. 46, for “( See section 3)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1987).`
