  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_58_footnotes
  sourcePage 58
obj_root_law_sections_58_content:
  string
  line 58
  line `( g ) the aggregate of the book profits for the five accounting years so arrived at, divided by 5,`
  line `shall be the maintainable profits of the company.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this rule, “interlocked companies” means any two investment`
  line `companies each of which holds shares in the other company.]`
  line ______
obj_root_law_sections_58_footnotes:
